- [ ] Google Calendar integration for event reminders
- [ ] Social sharing (WhatsApp, Twitter, Facebook) for event promotion
- [ ] Referral and discount code system
- [ ] Analytics dashboard with charts (using Recharts or Victory)
- [ ] Multi-currency support (NGN, USD, etc.)
- [ ] Mobile app (React Native) for organizers/check-in

---
*This plan provides a structured approach to building Gater.ng with Next.js, Prisma, and PostgreSQL. Adjust timelines based on team size and complexity. Regular reviews and iterations recommended.*